  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ReaderSQLSource
    An SQLSource that reads statements from a Reader.

    Exception Description
    SQLInputException

    An exception thrown by an SQLSource when the resource cannot be found.

Package org.soulwing.sql.source Description

SQL source code input support

This package provides supporting classes for reading SQL statements from files or other resources that can be located using a URL.
